layout.house_prompt: A large family home with a master bedroom, two kids bedrooms, a living room, a kitchen, a dining room, a hallway, and two bathrooms. The master bedroom has a bed with two nightstands and a dresser. The first kids bedroom has a bed and a desk with a chair. The second kids bedroom has a bunk bed and a bookshelf with books. The living room has a sofa, a coffee table, and a TV. The kitchen has a refrigerator, a stove, and a dining table with four chairs. The dining room has a dining table with six chairs and a sideboard. The hallway has a coat rack and a mirror on the wall. The first bathroom has a toilet, a sink, and a bathtub. The second bathroom has a toilet and a sink.
